title: Pro Football Hall of Famer Sonny Jurgensen dies at 91

sources.title: Pro Football Hall of Famer Sonny Jurgensen dies at 91
sources.description: The family of Pro Football Hall of Famer Sonny Jurgensen announced on Friday that he has died at the age of 91.
